# CLAUDE.local.md — machine-local notes (EXAMPLE)
#
# Copy to CLAUDE.local.md and fill in. CLAUDE.local.md is gitignored:
# it may reference credential NAMES/locations but must NEVER contain a
# secret value itself.

## Signing (user-held; scripts ask before using)

- Developer ID identity: Developer ID Application: YOUR NAME (TEAMID)
- notarytool keychain profile name: macsip-notary
  (created once with: xcrun notarytool store-credentials macsip-notary)

## Local test environment

- TestPBX host: 127.0.0.1 (docker compose in TestPBX/)
- Test extensions in use on this machine: 101, 102, 103
- Real-device manual tests available here: built-in mic/speakers, USB
  headset <model>, Bluetooth headset <model>

## Machine quirks

- (e.g. corporate VPN blocks UDP 5060 — use TCP transport for local tests)
